No, boat slips are paid separately due to limited number of slips.
<h4>Can I park my boat at my campsite?</h4>
No, we have boat/trailer parking across the road. Overnight boat docking is available, $18.00 per night.
<h4>What credit cards do you accept?</h4>
Visa and Master Card only.
<h4>Do you allow pets? How many?</h4>
Yes, two. <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>MUST</strong></span>Â  be on 6 ft. leash at all times.
<h4>Do you offer long-term rates?</h4>
We offer weekly on all sites and monthly on interior sites. No monthly on water front sites.
<h4>Can I check in early?</h4>
Yes, if your site is available.
<h4>What is the max number of people per site?</h4>
Six.
<h4>Will I be guaranteed the lot I requested?</h4>
Yes, as long as you have confirmed your reservation and paid your deposit for the site you requested.Â However, management reserves the right to move inner lot campers down one direction or the other if necessary to maximize occupancy.
<h4>How far in advance do I have to cancel my reservation?</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">There is a 7 day cancellation for nightly and weekly reservations.
There is a 14 day cancellation for monthly reservations.
Cancellations after notice requirement, loss of deposit.</p>

<h4>Will the payment come out of my account when I arrive or at the time of booking?</h4>
A 50% deposit is required at the time the reservation is made and the remaining balance will automatically run the day after the last cancellation date if a cancellation is not made.
<h4>Do you have a laundry facility?</h4>
Yes, coin operated located on 2nd floor of Clubhouse.
<h4>Do you have Wi-Fi and Cable TV?</h4>
Yes, we have Wi-Fi (password available at check-in) and Cable TV including ESPN channels.
<h4>Do we have to park across the road?</h4>
Your camper and twoÂ vehicles are allowed per campsite. All additional vehicles and boats will be parked across the road.
<h4>Can we make a small fire at our RV site?</h4>
Approved Fire Pits only.
<h4>Do you offer full hook-ups?</h4>
Yes, 30 and 50 amp, Cable TV, Â and sewer hookup at each site.
<h4>Do you have group rates?</h4>
We can custom price for large groups per request.
<h4>Is the pool heated?</h4>
Pool heated certain times of the year.
<h4>Do you have RV and boat storage?</h4>
Yes, across the road, uncovered.
<h4>What cities are you close to?</h4>
The closest towns are Port St. Joe, 4.5 miles, Apalachicola, 23 miles, and Mexico Beach, 17 miles. The closest cities are Panama City, 41 miles, and Tallahassee, 105 miles.
<h4>Do you have rental options if I do not own an RV?</h4>
Yes, we have a Two Bedroom Cottage and 3 One-Bedroom and 1 Two-Bedroom Park Models. Cleaning fees are not included in the nightly rates and are: $25 up to 3 nights, $50 for a weekly stay and $150 for a monthly stay.
<h4>Do you have boat rentals?</h4>
Yes, 20 ft. bay skiffs, pontoons, kayaks and paddle boards.
